Employers are obliged: to enable remote work or all employees whose work can be done from home; a separate decision on remote work has to be issued to each employee; all employees working from home must be recorded; where remote work is not possible, work should be, if possible, organized in shifts, and employer must provide protective equipment;
 enable business meetings to be held electronically (video link, video call, etc);
 postpone official travel in the country and abroad;
 Source: https://bdkadvokati.com/covid-19-update-serbia-montenegro-bosnia-and-herzegovina-2/

